<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('./head', { title: "About this project" }); %>
</head>
<body class="container">

<header>
    <%- include('./header'); %>
</header>

<main>
    <div class="project">
    <h2>About this project</h2>
     <p>
         The purpose of this project is to enable the users to exchange their used books with other users.
         <br> The only needed payment is for the Post, if necessary.  
         <br>This platform can be useful for people who like to read a lot, but they live in a small apartment. So, they cannot keep all their books. 
         <br>Also, this platform has financial benefits for the users, since they donâ€™t need to buy expensive first-hand books.
         <br>Each user has its own profile, and each book has a detail page to describe its contents and conditions.  
         <br>Users also can leave comments and reviews after the transaction is completed.
     </p>
     </div>
     
     <h2 style="text-align:center">How does it work</h2>
      <div class="about">
      <p>You search for the book<br>
          <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
      </p>
      <p>Agree with the owner<br>
          <i class="far fa-handshake"></i>
      </p>
      <p>Share books you want to give away<br>
          <i class="fas fa-recycle"></i>
      </p>
      </div>

      <!--Create account sugestion-->
      <div class="sugestion">
         <p>And do not forget to share your books</p>
         <button onclick="openSignupForm()">Create account</button>
      </div>
</main>

<footer>
    <%- include('./footer'); %>
</footer>

<style> 

body {
    background-image: linear-gradient( rgba(171,147,83,0), rgba(171, 148, 83, 0.3));

}
    .project {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 20px;
    }

    .about {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center; 
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
}

.about p {
    border: 1px solid #565656;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin: 30px 40px;
    width: 180px;
    height: 200px;
    padding: 25px;
}

.about i {
    font-size: 42px;
    margin-top: 35px;
}

/*Create account sugestion*/
.sugestion {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-top: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}
.sugestion button {
    background-color: #AB9353;
    color: #fdfbf3;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Hieu - popup - sign up */

.popup-signup-form *, .popup-login-form * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.popup-signup-form, .popup-login-form {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0px;
    z-index: 8;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: auto;
}

.signup-form, .login-form {
    width: 1024px;
    height: 830px;
    padding: 20px 300px;
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}

.signup-form h2, .login-form h2 {
    line-height: 33px;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-align: center;
}

.signup-form label, .login-form label {
    float: left;
    width: 32%;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.signup-form input[type=text],
.signup-form input[type=password],
.login-form input[type=text],
.login-form input[type=password] {
    width: 68%;
    padding: 15px 0 5px 15px;
    margin: 5px 0 15px 0;
    border: none;
    background-color: #ddd;
}

.signup-form input[type=text]:focus,
.signup-form input[type=password]:focus,
.login-form input[type=text]:focus,
.login-form input[type=password]:focus {
    background-color: rgb(207, 207, 207);
    outline: none;
}

.signup-form .btn, .login-form .btn {
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    color: var(--white-color);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 18px;
}

.signup-form .btn.signup, .login-form .btn.login {
    margin-top: 10px;
}

.signup-form .cancel, .login-form .cancel {
    background-color: red;
}

.signup-form .btn:hover,
.signup-button:hover,
.login-form .btn:hover,
.login-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
}

</style>



</body>
</html>